mechanical engineering from the indian institute of technology in delhi and an mba from the indian institute of management in ahmedabad “it’s been an honor and a pleasure to have been part of the team over the last four years and i am very proud of what we have accomplished” said chaomei chen “i wish continued success for sandeep and the team”     sponsored links by dq promote you may also likelending club announces new partnership with citibank for community lendinglending club  us women’s chamber of commerce form partnership to aid womenowned businesseslending club adds another partnership with score as it pushes further into business loansbuilding business lending club grows sme finance vertical with new line of credit productlending club announces new partnership with home improvement marketplace homeadvisor community banks partner up with lending club in pp pushyirendai appoints chaomei chen former chief risk officer of lendingclub as member of yirendai advisory committeelending club  union bank create strategic alliancelending club raises interest rates by 5 matching fedlending club launches aa super prime loans offers expanded options and lower rateslending club reacts to concerns over madden vs midland decisionlending club ipo priced at  share as early investors book huge gainslending club settles with consumer financial protection bureau on borrower confusion associated with springstone financialgrowing up lending club has been tested survived  is getting biggerwatch lending club ceo renaud laplanche testifies before house committee on small business tweet share share 1 reddit pin emailshares  pingback former capital one credit officer sandeep bhandari joins lending club as chief credit officer  movenergy subscribe to our weekly email email address sponsored links by dq promote    bhandari sandeep   facebook facebook？english us한국어français francebahasa indonesiapolskiespañolportuguês brasildeutschitalianomessengerfacebook liteinstagramcookie facebook  17